# Ignore File Management

## Critical Ignore Patterns

- `/docs/` - All documentation (reference only)
- `/data/documentation/` - Template documentation
- `node_modules/`, `dist/`, `build/`
- `*.min.js`, `*.min.css` - Minified files
- `.env.local`, `.env.*.local`

## Bloat Prevention Patterns

- `/dev/` - Development artifacts
- `/.specify/` - Workflow templates
- `/.agentic/` - Agent-generated files
- `/.cursorrules/` - Custom Cursor configs
- `/archive/` - Archived content
- `cursor_project_status_and_next_steps.md`

## File Size Limits

- Ignore files > 1MB in assets
- Ignore video files in documentation
- Ignore large template files
- Ignore generated documentation

## Always Require Secondary Approval

- **NEVER** modify ignore files without explicit user approval
- **ALWAYS** ask for confirmation before changing ignore patterns
- **ALWAYS** explain why ignore changes are needed
- **NEVER** override this requirement
